        {
            "_id": "3C3zNfr23ZOfVvUr",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "False Vision",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The potted violet etheroot can trigger a false vision as the hallucination spell (@Check[type:will|dc:26]) in the mind of a target within 800 feet to hear and see an object, creature, or force of the etheroot's choice, which can draw upon the target's own understanding. For example, the etheroot would not have to be familiar with the target's father to create a hallucination of the target's father that looked and sounded like him. The false vision can be sustained up to 1 hour.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
